  <name>LibreMines</name>
  <summary>A Free/Libre and Open Source Software Qt based Minesweeper game</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      LibreMines is a Free/Libre and Open Source Qt based Minesweeper game available for 
      GNU/Linux, FreeBSD, macOS and Windows systems.
    </p>
    <p>
      The game includes classic minesweeper gameplay with modern enhancements such as:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Multiple minefield themes (classic, alternative, flowerfield, twemoji)</li>
      <li>Customizable face reaction themes</li>
      <li>Sound effects</li>
      <li>Keyboard play mode</li>
      <li>Score tracking</li>
      <li>Cross-platform compatibility</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

